## How This Vault Is Organized
This is my second brain / knowledge base, managed in Obsidian. Full map: [[Meta/Vault-Map]].
- **Inbox/** — quick captures, web clips, unprocessed notes (default drop for new notes).
- **Projects/** — active, time-bound work.
- **Areas/** — ongoing life/work responsibilities (health, career, finances…).
- **Resources/** — evergreen reference material, docs, project docs.
- **Archive/** — completed projects and outdated notes.
- **Daily/** — daily resurfacing + seed-planting notes (see [[Meta/Sower]]).
- **Frontier/** — live seeds worth tracking long-term (see [[Meta/Sower]]).
- **Meta/** — system files, templates, and AI orientation files.

